We want something like this to work, similar to the [go]/etc. language-specific settings. Or some way for extensions to add it.

    "[cpp]": {
        "editor.acceptSuggestionOnEnter": false
    },
    "[c]": {
        "editor.acceptSuggestionOnEnter": false
    }

This matches the C++ completion behavior of Visual Studio, and it prevents annoying unwanted completions when a line ends with alphanumeric text and the intent is to go to the next line and not autocomplete.
